name: Wanita Kembang
description:
#6 | Ahmad Abi M Sidik | Nov 2021

The term Kota Kembang has always been attached to the identity of the city of Bandung, but in fact, in the city of Bandung, there are not many flowers? The meaning of the flower is beautiful women who live in Bandung, beautiful, elegant, pleasing to the eye like flowers.
